{"parse":{"title":"Edward Steers Jr.","pageid":2153886,"revid":849126824,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Edward Steers Jr.</b> is an American <a href=\"/wiki/Historian\" title=\"Historian\">historian</a> specializing in the <a href=\"/wiki/Abraham_Lincoln_assassination\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abraham Lincoln assassination\">assassination of President Abraham Lincoln</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-LOCBIO_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-LOCBIO-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Career\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Career</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Books\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Books</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Career\">Career</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Edward_Steers_Jr.&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Career\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Steers worked as a research scientist at the <a href=\"/wiki/National_Institutes_of_Health\" title=\"National Institutes of Health\">National Institutes of Health</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Bethesda,_Maryland\" title=\"Bethesda, Maryland\">Bethesda, Maryland</a> for thirty-two years until he retired in 1994 and started a new career as a writer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-LOCBIO_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-LOCBIO-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\nEdward Steers Jr. (University of Pennsylvania, AB, PhD) is the leading authority on the assassination of Abraham Lincoln. He has authored or edited eight books on Lincoln\u2019s death including <i>Blood on the Moon, The Lincoln Assassination Conspirators, His Name is Still Mudd, The Trial, The Lincoln Assassination. The Evidence, and The Lincoln Assassination Encyclopedia.</i> His book <i>Blood on the Moon</i> alleges that the Confederate Secret Service was intimately involved with John Wilkes Booth ultimately leading to the <a href=\"/wiki/Assassination_of_Abraham_Lincoln\" title=\"Assassination of Abraham Lincoln\">assassination of Abraham Lincoln</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Books\">Books</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Edward_Steers_Jr.&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Books\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em;float: right; clear: right; margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em\"><caption>External video</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;text-align: left\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/16px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/24px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/32px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"128\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/?168016-1/blood-moon\"><i>Booknotes</i> interview with Steers on <i>Blood on the Moon</i>, February 17, 2002</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/C-SPAN\" title=\"C-SPAN\">C-SPAN</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;text-align: left\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/16px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/24px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/32px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"128\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/?169291-4/blood-moon\">Presentation by Steers on <i>Blood on the Moon</i>, March 16, 2002</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/C-SPAN\" title=\"C-SPAN\">C-SPAN</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;text-align: left\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/16px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/24px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/32px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"128\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/?190117-6/trial-assassination-president-lincoln\">Presentation by Steers on <i>The Trial: The Assassination of President Lincoln</i>, November 17, 2005</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/C-SPAN\" title=\"C-SPAN\">C-SPAN</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;text-align: left\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/16px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/24px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg/32px-Nuvola_apps_kaboodle.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"128\" data-file-height=\"128\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.c-span.org/video/?293342-1/lincoln-assassination-encyclopedia\">Presentation by Steers on <i>The Lincoln Assassination Encyclopedia</i>, April 24, 2010</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/C-SPAN\" title=\"C-SPAN\">C-SPAN</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Steers is the author of a number of books, including:\n</p>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>The escape and capture of John Wilkes Booth</i>. Thomas Publications. 1992. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0939631490\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0939631490\">0939631490</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+escape+and+capture+of+John+Wilkes+Booth&amp;rft.pub=Thomas+Publications&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.isbn=0939631490&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>His name is still Mudd&#160;: the case against Doctor <a href=\"/wiki/Samuel_Alexander_Mudd\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Samuel Alexander Mudd\">Samuel Alexander Mudd</a></i>. Thomas Publications. 1997. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1577470192\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1577470192\">1577470192</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=His+name+is+still+Mudd+%3A+the+case+against+Doctor+Samuel+Alexander+Mudd&amp;rft.pub=Thomas+Publications&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.isbn=1577470192&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>The trial&#160;: the assassination of President Lincoln and the trial of the conspirators</i>. University Press of Kentucky. 2003. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0813122775\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0813122775\">0813122775</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+trial+%3A+the+assassination+of+President+Lincoln+and+the+trial+of+the+conspirators&amp;rft.pub=University+Press+of+Kentucky&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=0813122775&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>Blood on the Moon: The Assassination of Abraham Lincoln</i>. University Press of Kentucky. 2001. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0813122171\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0813122171\">0813122171</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Blood+on+the+Moon%3A+The+Assassination+of+Abraham+Lincoln&amp;rft.pub=University+Press+of+Kentucky&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.isbn=0813122171&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>Don't you know there's a war on?&#160;: life on the home front during World War II</i>. Sign of the Ox. 2007. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781577471288\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9781577471288\">9781577471288</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Don%27t+you+know+there%27s+a+war+on%3F+%3A+life+on+the+home+front+during+World+War+II&amp;rft.pub=Sign+of+the+Ox&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=9781577471288&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>The Lincoln Assassination. The Evidence</i>. University of Illinois Press. 2009. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780252033681\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780252033681\">9780252033681</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Lincoln+Assassination.+The+Evidence&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Illinois+Press&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.isbn=9780252033681&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\"><i>We'll meet again&#160;: a story about love and intrigue in the midst of war</i>. Publishamerica Inc. 2009. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1448966884\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1448966884\">1448966884</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=We%27ll+meet+again+%3A+a+story+about+love+and+intrigue+in+the+midst+of+war&amp;rft.pub=Publishamerica+Inc.&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.isbn=1448966884&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEdward+Steers+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"di